abstract: There’s a gender gap when it comes to earning, or wanting to earn, at the highest levels.
snippet: There’s a gender gap when it comes to earning, or wanting to earn, at the highest levels.
lead_paragraph: Women are running for political office in record numbers this year. They are challenging the sexual status quo from Hollywood to corporate offices, pursuing power as seldom before.

abstract: The Hudson Yards venue will feature programming across disciplines and include other luminaries from music, art, dance and theater.
snippet: The Hudson Yards venue will feature programming across disciplines and include other luminaries from music, art, dance and theater.
lead_paragraph: While the Shed’s unique architectural structure has been revealed, the plans for programming within have been more ambiguous. But on Wednesday, the Shed’s artistic director, Alex Poots, revealed the first batch of commissions for the Hudson Yards venue’s inaugural season.
